Sinnertwin continues plodding forward, and uses the momentum from his
run to avoid the grenades, and narowly the after shock. He then growls
as he notices his target has disapeared. He sniffs desperately for
something, then transforms and quickly fires his grenade towards the
smell. (I'm assuming you still smell when cloaked)
